title: Permits persons licensed to sell wine at retail for consumption on the premises to sell certain low alcohol beverages
summary: Permits persons licensed to sell wine at retail for consumption on the premises to sell certain low alcohol beverages that contain not more than twenty-four per centum alcohol, by volume, and that are produced from agricultural products.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to the sale of certain low alcohol beverages at retail for consumption on the premises
